channel.title: SMF 74 Subtype 10 on IBM SMF Explorer
channel.description: Recent content in SMF 74 Subtype 10 on IBM SMF Explorer

item.title: Field - _10cl
item.description: Length of SCM configuration measurement section Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF7410CL

item.title: Field - _10cn
item.description: Number of SCM configuration measurement sections Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF7410CN

item.title: Field - _10co
item.description: Offset to SCM configuration measurement sections Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF7410CO

item.title: Field - _10dl
item.description: Length of SCM EADM device information section Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF7410DL

item.title: Field - _10dn
item.description: Number of SCM EADM device information sections Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF7410DN

item.title: Field - _10do
item.description: Offset to SCM EADM device information section Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF7410DO

item.title: Field - bfy
item.description: SYSTEM RUNNING IN PR/SM MODE Record: SMF74S10 Based on: flg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 7 of field flg.

item.title: Field - boost_class
item.description: Boost class: 001 IPL, 010 Shutdown, 011 Recovery Process, Default: Unknown Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Post-Processed Flags postprocessor for multiple bit mapping.

item.title: Field - cne
item.description: Equipped with ESCON channel Map: SMF74PRO Based on: prf Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 1 of field prf.

item.title: Field - cnv
item.description: Data converted from version 2 Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 0 of field fla.

item.title: Field - cyc
item.description: Sampling cycle length 000TTTTF Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74CYC

item.title: Field - dat
item.description: Date monitor interval start: 00YYDDDF Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74DAT

item.title: Field - date
item.description: Date of Record Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74DTE

item.title: Field - drc
item.description: ESCON Director in configuration Map: SMF74PRO Based on: prf Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 2 of field prf.

item.title: Field - dte
item.description: DATE RECORD WRITTEN Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74DTE

item.title: Field - eed
item.description: Speed boost was active during entire interval Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 10 of field fla.

item.title: Field - eme
item.description: System in z/ARCH mode Map: SMF74PRO Based on: prf Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 3 of field prf.

item.title: Field - esa
item.description: MVS/ESA IF ON Record: SMF74S10 Based on: flg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 4 of field flg.

item.title: Field - fla
item.description: Flags Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74FLA Flag fields This is a flag field with the following bit fields: Field Bit-Position Description cnv 0 Data converted from version 2 iss 1 Invalid samples to be skipped m3r 2 Record was written by RMF Monitor III ism 3 Interval was under SMF control rcl 4 SMF record converted to lower service level. rch 5 SMF record converted to higher release or service level.

item.title: Field - flg
item.description: SYSTEM INDICATOR FLAGS Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74FLG Flag fields This is a flag field with the following bit fields: Field Bit-Position Description rrf 0 NEW RECORD FORMAT sut 1 SUBTYPES USED v4 3 MVS/ESA V4 IF ON esa 4 MVS/ESA IF ON vxa 5 MVS/XA IF ON os 6 OPERATING SYSTEM IS OS/VS2 bfy 7 SYSTEM RUNNING IN PR/SM MODE

item.title: Field - gie
item.description: Projected gathering interval end GMT time (STCK format) Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74GIE

item.title: Field - iet
item.description: Interval expiration time token Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74IET

item.title: Field - iip
item.description: zIIP boost was active during entire interval Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 9 of field fla.

item.title: Field - iml
item.description: Indicates the type of processor complex on which data measurements were taken. Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74IML Description X'03’ = 9672, zSeries

item.title: Field - int
item.description: Duration of monitor interval: MMSSTTTF Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74INT

item.title: Field - ism
item.description: Interval was under SMF control Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 3 of field fla.

item.title: Field - iss
item.description: Invalid samples to be skipped Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 1 of field fla.

item.title: Field - ist
item.description: TOD monitor interval start: 0HHMMSSF Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74IST

item.title: Field - len
item.description: SMF RECORD LENGTH. Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74LEN Description ZERO AFTER GRBSMFR REASSEMBLY

item.title: Field - lgo
item.description: Offset GMT to local time Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74LGO

item.title: Field - m3r
item.description: Record was written by RMF Monitor III Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 2 of field fla.

item.title: Field - mfv
item.description: RMF version number in packed decimal format: nnnF Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74MFV

item.title: Field - mvs
item.description: MVS software level (consists of an acronym and the version, release, and modification level - ZVvvrrmm) Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74MVS

item.title: Field - oil
item.description: Original interval length as defined in the session or by SMF (in seconds) Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74OIL

item.title: Field - os
item.description: OPERATING SYSTEM IS OS/VS2 Record: SMF74S10 Based on: flg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 6 of field flg.

item.title: Field - pe2
item.description: Enhanced DAT facility 2 Map: SMF74PRO Based on: prf Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 7 of field prf.

item.title: Field - ped
item.description: Enhanced DAT facility 1 Map: SMF74PRO Based on: prf Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 6 of field prf.

item.title: Field - prd
item.description: Product name Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74PRD

item.title: Field - prf
item.description: Processor flags Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74PRF Flag fields This is a flag field with the following bit fields: Field Bit-Position Description qes 0 System has expanded storage cne 1 Equipped with ESCON channel drc 2 ESCON Director in configuration eme 3 System in z/ARCH mode pri 4 At least one zAAP is currently installed prp 5 At least one zIIP is currently installed ped 6 Enhanced DAT facility 1 pe2 7 Enhanced DAT facility 2

item.title: Field - pri
item.description: At least one zAAP is currently installed Map: SMF74PRO Based on: prf Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 4 of field prf.

item.title: Field - prl
item.description: LENGTH OF RMF PRODUCT SECTION Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74PRL

item.title: Field - prn
item.description: NUMBER OF RMF PRODUCT SECTIONS Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74PRN

item.title: Field - prp
item.description: At least one zIIP is currently installed Map: SMF74PRO Based on: prf Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 5 of field prf.

item.title: Field - prs
item.description: OFFSET TO RMF PRODUCT SECTION Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74PRS

item.title: Field - ptn
item.description: PR/SM partition number Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74PTN

item.title: Field - qes
item.description: System has expanded storage Map: SMF74PRO Based on: prf Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 0 of field prf.

item.title: Field - r7410cdr
item.description: Data units read at LPAR level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CDR

item.title: Field - r7410cdrc
item.description: Data units read at CPC level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CDRC

item.title: Field - r7410cdus
item.description: Data unit size in bytes Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CDUS

item.title: Field - r7410cdw
item.description: Data units written at LPAR level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CDW

item.title: Field - r7410cdwc
item.description: Data units written at CPC level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CDWC

item.title: Field - r7410ciqc
item.description: Accumulated IOP queue time in units of 128 microseconds at CPC level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CIQC

item.title: Field - r7410cpid
item.description: Part identifier Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CPID

item.title: Field - r7410crid
item.description: SCM resource identifier Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CRID

item.title: Field - r7410crq
item.description: Internal requests processed at LPAR level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CRQ

item.title: Field - r7410crqc
item.description: Internal requests processed at CPC level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CRQC

item.title: Field - r7410crt
item.description: Aggregate time spent on execution of requests involving resource part in units of 128 microseconds at LPAR level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CRT

item.title: Field - r7410crtc
item.description: Aggregate time spent on execution of requests involving resource part in units of 128 microseconds at CPC level Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CRTC

item.title: Field - r7410cwu
item.description: Utilization at LPAR level. Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CWU Description This value designates the sum of the average LPAR utilization per second in percent multiplied by the number of seconds of this interval

item.title: Field - r7410cwuc
item.description: Utilization at CPC level. Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410CWUC Description This value designates the sum of the average CPC utilization per second in percent multiplied by the number of seconds of this interval

item.title: Field - r7410dcrt
item.description: Sum of initial command response times across all devices in units of 128 microseconds (doubleword format). Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DCRT Description The time from when the first command does not immediately proceed to execute until the successful start of execution at the SCM resource part.

item.title: Field - r7410dflg
item.description: Device information flags Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DFLG Flag fields This is a flag field with the following bit fields: Field Bit-Position Description r7410ecpr 0 EADM-compression-measurements facility available

item.title: Field - r7410dfpt
item.description: Sum of function pending times across all devices in units of 128 microseconds (doubleword format). Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DFPT Description The time lapse between the SSCH being issued and the acceptance of the first command of the channel program at the device.

item.title: Field - r7410diqt
item.description: Sum of IOP queue times across all devices in units of 128 microseconds (doubleword format). Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DIQT Description The amount of time the request is not accepted at the SCM resource because it would exceed its maximum capacity.

item.title: Field - r7410disc
item.description: Number of 1M input blocks consumed for compression Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DISC

item.title: Field - r7410disd
item.description: Number of 1M input blocks consumed for decompression Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DISD

item.title: Field - r7410dnum
item.description: Number of updates to the time accumulation fields Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DNUM

item.title: Field - r7410docc
item.description: Number of compression operations Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DOCC

item.title: Field - r7410docd
item.description: Number of decompression operations Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DOCD

item.title: Field - r7410dosc
item.description: Number of 1M output blocks consumed for compression Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DOSC

item.title: Field - r7410dosd
item.description: Number of 1M output blocks consumed for decompression Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DOSD

item.title: Field - r7410dsct
item.description: SSCH count across all devices Map: R7410DI Based on: R7410DSCT

item.title: Field - r7410ecpr
item.description: EADM-compression-measurements facility available Map: R7410DI Based on: r7410dflg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 0 of field r7410dflg.

item.title: Field - r7410flg
item.description: Flag byte Map: R7410CM Based on: R7410FLG Flag fields This is a flag field with the following bit fields: Field Bit-Position Description r7410vfm 0 SCM resource type is VFM

item.title: Field - r7410vfm
item.description: SCM resource type is VFM Map: R7410CM Based on: r7410flg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 0 of field r7410flg.

item.title: Field - ral
item.description: Length of reassembly area. Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74RAL Description Area consists of a fixed header and a variable number of information blocks. Length depends on the record type/subtype, but is fixed for a specific type/subtype

item.title: Field - ran
item.description: Number of reassembly area. Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74RAN Description This field is used to indicate whether SMF record is broken. If 0, record is not broken. If 1, record is broken. Offset and length are only valid if SMFxxRAN is 1. Reassembly area is only present in broken records.

item.title: Field - rao
item.description: Offset to reassembly area relative to start of RMF product section Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74RAO

item.title: Field - rch
item.description: SMF record converted to higher release or service level. Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Description Bit is set by SMF record retrieval service GRBSMFR. Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 5 of field fla.

item.title: Field - rcl
item.description: SMF record converted to lower service level. Map: SMF74PRO Based on: fla Description Bit is set by SMF record retrieval service GRBSMFR. Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 4 of field fla.

item.title: Field - rrf
item.description: NEW RECORD FORMAT Record: SMF74S10 Based on: flg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 0 of field flg.

item.title: Field - rty
item.description: RECORD TYPE Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74RTY

item.title: Field - sam
item.description: Number of samples Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74SAM

item.title: Field - seg
item.description: SEGMENT DESCRIPTOR Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74SEG

item.title: Field - sid
item.description: SYSTEM ID FROM INSTALLATION Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74SID

item.title: Field - snm
item.description: System name for current system as defined in CVTSNAME Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74SNM

item.title: Field - srl
item.description: SMF record level Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74SRL

item.title: Field - ssi
item.description: SUBSYSTEM ID (RMF ) Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74SSI

item.title: Field - sty
item.description: SUBTYPE Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74STY

item.title: Field - sut
item.description: SUBTYPES USED Record: SMF74S10 Based on: flg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 1 of field flg.

item.title: Field - syn
item.description: SYNC value in seconds Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74SYN

item.title: Field - time
item.description: Time of Record Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74TME

item.title: Field - timestamp
item.description: Record Timestamp Record: SMF74S10 Based on: date, time Description Timestamp from SMF data Post-Processed This field is combined from a date and a time field to form a timestamp.

item.title: Field - tme
item.description: TOD RECORD WRITTEN Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74TME

item.title: Field - trn
item.description: NUMBER OF TRIPLETS IN THIS REC Record: SMF74S10 Based on: SMF74TRN

item.title: Field - v4
item.description: MVS/ESA V4 IF ON Record: SMF74S10 Based on: flg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 3 of field flg.

item.title: Field - vxa
item.description: MVS/XA IF ON Record: SMF74S10 Based on: flg Post-Processed This virtual field corresponds to the flag at bit-position 5 of field flg.

item.title: Field - xnm
item.description: Sysplex name as defined in ECVTSPLX Map: SMF74PRO Based on: SMF74XNM
